                   <h3>How can you block or delete cookies?</h3>
                   <p>Do you prefer that LTO Network not place any cookies at all on your device? You can block or delete these cookies yourself via the privacy settings of your browser. The website may as a consequence function less optimal, or even not function at all. See the explanation above for "necessary cookies".</p>
                   </div>
