                   <h3>Block cookies</h3>
                   <p>Do you want to prevent new cookies from being placed? You can turn off the possibility that cookies are stored on your computer, tablet or mobile. There are various ways to block cookies. You can block all cookies, block a specific type of cookie or block cookies from certain websites. You can do this yourself through the privacy settings of your browser. When cookies are blocked, all cookies remain that were already present on your computer, tablet or mobile. Itâ€™s best therefore to remove all your already placed cookies in addition to blocking.</p>
                   </div>
               </div>
            </div>
            
